                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17810425-56-off271 t17810425-56-cd272"></join>, three gold shirt-buckles, value 12 s. eight stone shirt-buckles set in silver, value 12 s. a silver stone sleeve-button, value 2 s. a silver seal, value 3 s.
